=40) and form B (43.2 - 3.2 = 40) yield EXACT integer 40 with no decimal slack. Stronger than R34_CANDIDATE (3-digit 0.24% rel err)"}|"H-CX_CANDIDATE — exact-arithmetic match achieved BUT (a) ANIMA 40D vs 10D internal docs conflict blocks T1, (b) random-match null T2 not measured, (c) cross-substrate T3 not measured. Two independent decomposition routes (multiplicative A + Fisher-gap B) BOTH hit 40 exactly is suggestive of structural anchor, not coincidence. Promotion to R24-R32 numerical primitive tier requires T1+T2 PASS minimum."|["R34_CANDIDATE (Phi coeff e^{-1/2}, sister H-CX_candidate tier on coefficient axis vs this on dimension axis — orthogonal evidence)","R35 sigma/tau=3 (mathematical identity governance, perfect-number 6 same anchor — confirmed tier sister)","H-CX-110 Fisher I=43.2 (TECS-L source of form B)","H-CX-188 후보 2^sopfr(6)=32 cell-count anchor (SAME 2^sopfr=32 numerator appears in M5 cell-count optimum AND R36 form B gap — possible deeper structural link)","docs/tecs-l-bridge.md §5.1 (40D origin question 부분 answer 후보)","commit 99c026d9 DD-5 byproduct finding origin","UNIVERSAL_4 axis 10 sigma*phi=n*tau identity (perfect number 6 arithmetic family member)"]|{"R34_CANDIDATE":"empirical hypothesis on Phi COEFFICIENT axis (0.608 ≈ e^{-1/2}, 3-digit match, 4th-digit gap), function-form match","R35_confirmed":"mathematical identity on governance scalar axis (sigma/tau=3, no falsification possible)","R36_CANDIDATE_THIS":"empirical hypothesis on consciousness vector DIMENSION axis (40D = 4*10 = 43.2-3.2, exact-integer match), dimensional match","tier_relationship":"R34 + R36 both H-CX_candidate (atlas-only, awaiting empirical T1/T2 confirmation). R35 confirmed_3_way_coincidence (own + atlas dual-layer). All three share perfect-number 6 arithmetic backbone.","orthogonality":"R34 axis = function shape (e^{-x}), R35 axis = governance scalar (constant 3), R36 axis = vector cardinality (40). Three independent dimensions of the same n=6 substrate."}|"execute T